<br>
Gorn, do you not listen?  I didnt really care about the shoulders, only reason i brought it up was i figured, &quot;if we're gonna take a faction hit, lets take a faction hit&quot;.  I left because you wouldnt @#%$ listen to me about the faction issue.  <br>
<br>
I did not complain about loot all the time.  Only time i complained about not killing a mob was when we were right next to Maestro in Hate, and Iron was insisting on killing Velk.... didnt make much sense to me... and that was the only reason i brought it up.  <br>
<br>
When i expressed my concern, you should not have brushed me off.  You should not have told me to STFU.  that is, if you wanted me, and the SS armor on me to stay.  Up until the point you told me to STFU i had no intention of leaving the guild.  It was YOU and Ironlute that caused me to leave.  You were right to trust me with the armor.  But when you start pulling this BS, you cannot expect anyone to stay, especially after you insult them the way you did me in guild chat.  <br>
<br>
You keep bringing up this other MA thing.  Yes, there was a disagreement, those happen, welcome to life gorn.  But it hasnt been an issue for well over 2 months.  <br>
<br>
The reason i left was not because i didnt get loot.  A small part of it had to do with the way some loot was handled (loot totally unrelated to me btw, so you cant call me a loot whore on that one), but over all the way you,.... nm the way Iron runs your guild.  And they way you addressed valid concerns brought up by one of your guild members, that was shared by others, tho they did not speak up (i recieved two tells to this effect, no i didnt take any SSs was too flustered about being chased out of the guild).<br>
<br>
What gets me on top of all this, the night i deguilded, i recieved no /tells from you at all before or after.  After i recieved one from Iron asking for the guild owned equipmenti had.  i told her i had none.  She said what about the UP weapons?  My response: What UP weapons?  The ones that would be No drop if i had them?  Way to @#%$ know how to gear your MTs/guild.  All she was concerned with was loot, not trying to work the issue out.... real nice and classy....<br>
<br>
Gorn, you are teh best raid leader i have ever seen.  But your methods of running a guild are lacking, as pointed out by numerous people, all pointing to the same issues.  I could see it if it was a few isolated incidents.  But you have many many people (reputable people for the most part) all saying the same thing.  That should give you pause to stop and think that maybe, even if some of what the say is wrong, just maybe there might be a grain of truth in something they are saying.<br>
<br>
I hope RE can be successful, but atm, i know of several people considering leaving... that should give you pause as well.  It does not look to me like RE will last at its current str much longer. And that saddens me.<br>
<br>
You can say that i left because of loot, becuase at the surface it looks that way, but wtf would i leave a guild that i got a full suit of SS in, over a shoulder peice that can be bought.  I am not stupid, and that would be a stupid thing to do especially if i was a &quot;loot whore&quot;.  <br>
<br>
Something i have noticed through this thread you have not denied with any sort of proof several of the accusations made.  Whether you chose to do this, or whether you have no proof, it does not look good for you Gorn.  If you have no proof, that to should give you pause to stop and think.<br>
<br>
Several people here have given multiple examples of what we are talking about, all indicating the same thing.  This should also give you pause.  <br>
<br>
There is definately something wrong Gorn, i dont think even you can deny that.  <br>
<br>
I think the best thing for RE would be for you to step down as the leader (not as a raid leader, you are the best at that) and let someone else handle guild issues while you handle raids.  But that is just my opinion and almost certainly wont happen.  <br>
<br>
I really hate to see all the work so many people have put into RE be for nothing if it implodes like it is looking to me atm. <br>
